06-cloche-init-design.md-10-ignores `.cloche/*/` then negates specific subdirectories, which means any new\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-cloche-init-design.md-11-directory added to `.cloche/` is accidentally ignored until explicitly whitelisted.\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-cloche-init-design.md-12-\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-cloche-init-design.md-13-## New `.gitignore` strategy\n--\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-cloche-init-design.md-50-```\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-cloche-init-design.md-51-.cloche/\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-cloche-init-design.md-52-  config.toml          # project settings (new)\ndocs/plans/2026-03-06-cloche-init-design.md-53-  version              # project version counter, content: \"1\" (new)\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-cloche-init-design.md-54-  <workflow>.cloche    # container workflow definition (existing)\ndocs/plans/2026-03-06-cloche-init-design.md:55:  host.cloche          # host orchestration workflow (new)\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-cloche-init-design.md-56-  Dockerfile           # container image (existing)\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-cloche-init-design.md-57-  prompts/\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-cloche-init-design.md-58-    implement.md       # (existing)\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-cloche-init-design.md-59-    fix.md             # (existing)\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-cloche-init-design.md-60-    update-docs.md     # (existing)\n--\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-cloche-init-design.md-85-\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-cloche-init-design.md-86-```\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-cloche-init-design.md-87-1\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-cloche-init-design.md-88-```\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-cloche-init-design.md-89-\ndocs/plans/2026-03-06-cloche-init-design.md:90:### `host.cloche` content\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-cloche-init-design.md-91-\ndocs/plans/2026-03-06-cloche-init-design.md-92-See host workflow design doc. The default replicat