s/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md-168-6. On goroutine return: decrement in-flight, update task state (success/fail)\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md-169-\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md-170-The old `promptGen` and `dispatch` are still used as the **fallback** when\ndocs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md:171:`host.cloche` is absent (no breaking change for existing projects).\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md-172-\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md-173-`WaitRun` needs access to the run store. Wire it in `initOrchestrator` in\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md-174-`cmd/cloched/main.go`.\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md-175-\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md-176----\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md-177-\ndocs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md:178:## Default `host.cloche` (from `cloche init`)\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md-179-\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md-180-```\ndocs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md:181:# host.cloche — orchestration workflow (runs on host, not in container)\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md-182-# Steps here execute as the daemon user. Keep operations simple and safe.\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md-183-\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md-184-workflow \"main\" {\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md-185-  step prepare-prompt {\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md-186-    run     = \"bash .cloche/scripts/prepare-prompt.sh\"\n--\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md-227-\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md-228-## Safety notes\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md-229-\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md-230-- Host steps run with the same OS privileges as the `cloched` process.\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md-231-- No network isolation.\ndocs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md:232:- `host.cloche` should only reference scripts that are committed to the project.\ndocs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md:233:- Document that `prompt` steps in `host.cloche` invoke an LLM agent with full host\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md-234-  filesystem access — use judiciously.\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md-235-\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md-236----\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md-237-\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md-238-## Changes required\n--\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md-240-| File | Change |\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md-241-|------|--------|\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md-242-| `internal/domain/workflow.go` | Add `StepTypeWorkflow`, add `workflow_name`/`prompt_step` to `knownStepConfigKeys` |\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md-243-| `internal/dsl/parser.go` | Infer `StepTypeWorkflow` when `workflow_name` key is present |\ndocs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md-244-| `internal/orchestrator/hostrunner.go` | New: host workflow executor |\ndocs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md:245:| `internal/orchestrator/orchestrator.go` | Refactor `Run()` to use `HostRunner` when `host.cloche` exists; fall back to current behavior otherwise |\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md-246-| `internal/ports/container.go` | Add `RunWaiter` interface |\n/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md-247-| `cmd/cloched/main.go` | Wire `HostRunner` into orchestrator init |\ndocs/plans/2026-03-06-host-workflow-design.md:248:| `cmd/cloche/init.go` | Create `host.cloche` and `scr